.org.il/news/160853\">נציגי חב\"ד: אלו שנכנסו למועצות ואלו שלא, בחירות מקומיות תשפ\"ד</a> <span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/index.php/%D7%97%D7%91%22%D7%93_%D7%90%D7%95%D7%9F_%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%99%D7%9F\" title=\"חב&quot;ד און ליין\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/15px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"15\" height=\"15\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/23px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8c/%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg/30px-%D7%A1%D7%99_%D7%90%D7%95_%D7%90%D7%9C_%D7%A1%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%99%D7%9C.jpg 2x\" /></a></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414013212\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: [show‐toc]\nCPU time usage: 0.080 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.384 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 194/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 984/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 5/100\nExpensive parser function count: 1/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4731/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.050/7 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5746688/52428800 bytes\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  333.846      1 -total\n 86.34%  288.255      5 תבנית:הערה\n 10.67%   35.610      1 תבנית:הערות_שוליים\n  4.45%   14.849      3 תבנית:COL\n  2.73%    9.128      1 תבנית:אינפו\n  1.34%    4.479      1 תבנית:הערות_שוליים/מרחב_שם\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key chabadped_1-infopedia_:pcache:idhash:65761-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414013212 and revision id 809702. Rendering was triggered because: page-view\n -->\n</div>"
